}
```

#### Response

```json
{
  "id": "5d6a8d48-b45c-43d8-9b0d-5cc3bd110001",
  "groupName": "Marketing Team",
  "createdAt": "2026-04-15T08:20:00.000Z",
  "updatedAt": "2026-04-15T08:20:00.000Z"
}
```

#### Error cases
- `400`: validation error
- `401`: missing/invalid JWT
- `403`: role is not `ADMIN`
